data.description:
End unit, 3 bedrooms and full master bath and full hallway bath upstairs,
First floor: living room, country kitchen with enough space for dining table and separate breakfast table area  or other possible creative furniture arrangements...and a guest bathroom.  The basement is finished (except laundry room) and has fireplace and a guest bath.  Bi level deck and privacy fence  on rear.
data.whatILove: This is an end unit, level lot, with a reliably dry finished basement with fireplace. The local elementary school is close enough to watch your kids walk across the field to school from the kitchen window or deck. Close to 4 grocery stores, 3 gas stations, schools, Upper Marlboro court house, library and post office just 5 miles away, and another nearby post office in Cheltenham, nearby rural areas, and close enough to D.C., Waldorf, the new Harbor Place, Annapolis, Baltimore for a wide variety of shopping and events.  Very close to gorgeous 7000+ acre Patuxent River Park with biking,hiking, camping, canoeing, kayaking, and fishing.
